{"h6249bc58ga2d2g4fd2gb6e7g3919121397d6": ["Finally. A city full of <i>real</i> coin.", "e1fda08b-45d4-41db-84b5-20e9931ba5af", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_PickpocketTrader.html", "8a07e476-0ab6-a609-2c2c-a78f855a12d8"], "h50af338bg15bdg4492gbab5g78ddab81b448": ["I'm... glad you didn't die. No discounts once I'm running the Wide in Baldur's Gate, mind.", "e1fda08b-45d4-41db-84b5-20e9931ba5af", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_PickpocketTrader.html", "9c445b3f-cd85-1f38-a36c-39baef8ec115"], "h7c4528c7g4c6bg4c46gb825gd9e8b7744614": ["Need something else?", "e1fda08b-45d4-41db-84b5-20e9931ba5af", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_PickpocketTrader.html", "3e8f2be7-a6f0-b666-ef29-22d94c84db35"], "hcb5d951bg0a41g4efbg987fg1d4d72c40cb7": ["Let's see what you have.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_PickpocketTrader.html", "47522b2b-d670-b0c4-9679-fec0bc1abe21"], "h122581beg1573g4452gbd36gb351af0fd78b": ["Thanks. Don't die.", "e1fda08b-45d4-41db-84b5-20e9931ba5af", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_PickpocketTrader.html", "8cdd5cdc-11a1-fb4a-b84a-6c08a03bab58"], "h0f03ed66g22d6g42f8gaa3agd95546375862": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_PickpocketTrader.html", "6e12b043-c9ae-b805-c26c-164513ba3e63"], "h4346da06gf873g4795g9786gf906327df361": ["Need anything before the fighting starts? No tricks this time, promise.", "e1fda08b-45d4-41db-84b5-20e9931ba5af", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_PickpocketTrader.html", "b11e45f2-0fdc-8339-dbfa-bb66c988c771"], "h01ee7b89gdbc6g483eg8c71g055f6faebbef": ["What about a discount? I'm about to risk my life.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_PickpocketTrader.html", "5fb3ddd9-f380-9035-9432-bdd6d8cf0c63"], "ha21ac989g5ac7g4872g98f3ge4da74896918": ["Huh. Fair enough. Can always get my money back when you're dead.", "e1fda08b-45d4-41db-84b5-20e9931ba5